{"id": "1295911054529921024", "channel_id": "1295911054529921024", "type": 0, "author_id": "190674373483429888", "author_name": ".weiyu", "author_bot": false, "content": "哇哩個豆啊，阿方索之器，你是要毀了我嗎？\n說好的把超維空間塞滿呢？\n沒人告訴過我你不認識躍遷啊\n\n目測目前實際效果為：隨機塞入驚厥、靈感五張，\n而非直到上限，與文本描述不符，要死了學校救我啊！", "timestamp": "2024-10-16T00:47:52.263000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-10-16T03:24:12.711000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😲", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}, {"emoji": "kyaru_confuse", "emoji_id": "948927649110188092", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "🥺", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1295911054936641627", "filename": "Screenshot_20241016_083427.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 202189, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1295911054529921024/1295911054936641627/Screenshot_20241016_083427.jpg?ex=6a007e78&is=69ff2cf8&hm=8dece28f97bea11308e43e52efeb29cdbe845ff3ea20a871b24a7f8bc7a02d2c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1295911054529921024", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "說好的塞滿呢？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1295944934423265292", "channel_id": "1295944934423265292", "type": 0, "author_id": "535870454116778004", "author_name": "mistvapour", "author_bot": false, "content": "基本上玩10分鐘會閃退一次，手機是i11，通常是在環拉開大的時候閃退，或是死亡吃靈芝的時候", "timestamp": "2024-10-16T03:02:29.859000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1295944934423265292", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "閃退", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1295911961904549980", "channel_id": "1295911961904549980", "type": 0, "author_id": "1001696859225591869", "author_name": "o5214658", "author_bot": false, "content": "目前這些兌換商店，金劵哪都能用到、沉澱跟深潛長期不足、無光至少還有四個命輪能慢慢疊+12；而調查兌換如果密契都各刷好一套，那就只剩下每週換幾枝筆了……\n\n現在調查兌換消耗遠遠低於獲取，看著那不停上升的數字、希望能增加些消耗品項；不然能多換幾枝筆也好啊！\n\n還是各位有什麼消耗辦法？\n目前印章感覺也不是很缺，而且換密契再換成印章手續又太多、很麻煩……", "timestamp": "2024-10-16T00:51:28.598000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💗", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1295911962420580392", "filename": "Screenshot_20241016-083933.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1682965, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1295911961904549980/1295911962420580392/Screenshot_20241016-083933.png?ex=6a007f50&is=69ff2dd0&hm=0ada8b3335cc6e9e794b4aa67bdc8eb9eb1b6bb128d0c13f02fe99b049324b50&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1295911961904549980", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "調查兌換商店品項能不能增加？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
